iproton signal from the decays of the\ngravitino LSP might be within the sensitivity of AMS-02 and gamma-ray\ntelescopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jul 2015 18:34:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-16"}
