sequence that UV luminosity density (and hence unobscured\nstar-formation density) peaks at z ~ 2.5 - 3, when the Universe was ~ 2.5 Gyr\nold.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jul 2015 20:01:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 6 Mar 2016 10:47:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-08"}
