\nrelated positive semidefinite matrices, $\\boldsymbol{X}^* \\boldsymbol{X} +\n\\lambda \\boldsymbol{I}_n$ and $\\boldsymbol{X} \\boldsymbol{X}^* + \\lambda\n\\boldsymbol{I}_m$ when $m > n$ or $m < n$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jul 2015 14:16:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 May 2017 23:30:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-15"}
